{"id": "1490815252642660402", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "author_id": "274853543934951425", "author_name": "morgaenrei", "content": "A bit more aggressive comp, but it's fun to play in the low ranks, since most of them don't know how to brick it.\n\nYou make Lotan your front-liner, and give her suction. Keep Ogier's ability *Knights Zeal* just in case she might get killed. He is tanky and can take a lot of beating. Doll is to keep front alive and Ramone to do damage and allow Lotan to snowball her strikes to do a lot of damage. Not the best, but I had a lot of fun with a different variation of it.\n\nSecond one is a bit more standard\n\nSame idea - main damage is Lotan in the back with frenzy - get it snowballing and don't let them brick her with util.\n\nYou can also replace lotan with shark and get even better comp, but in that case take the eyes to get more ael. \n\n\nc3raphile comps are objectively better, but here is the thing. Since they are better, they are stronger. Since they are stronger.... yeah, stronger opponents. Cause I just had this *exact* comp today and I run KaDe's little slaughterhouse on wheels at 1500-2000 ranks\n\nSo you might have a higher chances of meeting more serious opponents with it", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T20:47:34.238000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-06T20:48:36.590000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1490815251489226792", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2001694, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1326453691527594035/1490815251489226792/image.png?ex=69d56d65&is=69d41be5&hm=4488d6ce8c345702e24541caae1b6641a5212a325e16f315ca60e624c92644e5&"}, {"id": "1490815251971575808", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1993039, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1326453691527594035/1490815251971575808/image.png?ex=69d56d66&is=69d41be6&hm=f1d5aedcd255b77734b27af02c06f66750efa10a6cf4471924b51ed9272df970&"}, {"id": "1490815252349325393", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2067879, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1326453691527594035/1490815252349325393/image.png?ex=69d56d66&is=69d41be6&hm=a34e8216affe8e5a8769706f17df8fb5b81360be6e909ec2b31198d18224df7a&"}]}
